dialogue:
Why am I trying to get to [color=#b38b2b]Wonderland[/color], anyway? If leaving
[color=#b38b2b]Wonderland[/color] means abandoning my memories, what would I
want so badly outside of it?

I can't stay here long, or I may lose my memories entirely and
turn into a regular doll. But if there's something wrong with
[color=#b38b2b]Wonderland[/color]... should I even go home?
